overview: In its heyday, Changa Tuki, aka Raptor House, attracted thousands of young people to afternoon parties called "matinees", from those parties a controversial subculture grew, one that still echoes to this day. This is the story as told by its protagonists.
tagline: In the early 2000, in the slums of Caracas, a new style of dancing and electronic music was born.
title: Vamos Pal Matiné
